description:
 This check reports the number of connected clients per SSID and per AP.
 It evaluates:
  - Total number of clients
  - Clients per band (2.4 / 5 / 6 GHz)
  - Perâ€‘SSID association
 .
 State logic:
  - OK: Client data available and within expected ranges
  - WARN: Unusually high number of clients (threshold configurable)
  - CRIT: Client API reports invalid or missing values
  - UNKNOWN: No client information available

item:
 The SSID handled by the Access Point.

perfdata:
 Creates metrics:
  - total_clients
  - clients_24
  - clients_5
  - clients_6
